<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bar-n">bar <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɑː(r)/    美 /bɑːr/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>条；杆；棒；块：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a bar of</strong> chocolate / soap
一块巧克力/肥皂</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As the sun went down, there was <strong>a bar of</strong> red over the western hills. 
日落时分，一道红霞笼罩在西山上。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>酒吧；柜台：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a coffee / snack / wine bar</strong>
咖啡馆/小吃店/酒吧</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="behind-bars">behind bars</h3>
<p>1.<strong>坐牢</strong>  </p></div>